<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1543467-it-seems-like-there-are-a-lot-of-people">It seems like there are a lot of people who are criticizing this book. Which is fine it certainly has its flaws. I had fun the entire time I read it and was thoroughly entertained. So did anyone else just enjoy reading about zombie Nazis?</a>
